## Typography (`AppTextStyles`)

- **Display / Headlines:** Space Grotesk, bold
- **Body / Labels / Buttons:** Inter

| Style | Size | Weight | Use for |
|-------|------|--------|---------|
| `headlineLarge` | 24 w700 | Screen titles |
| `headlineMedium` | 20 w600 | Section headers, pushed screen AppBar |
| `headlineSmall` | 18 w600 | Card titles, dialog headers |
| `bodyLarge` | 16 w400 lh1.6 | Primary content |
| `bodyMedium` | 14 w400 lh1.5 | Secondary content |
| `bodySmall` | 12 w400 lh1.4 | Captions, helper text (`textSecondary`) |
| `labelLarge` | 14 w600 | Row labels, interactive |
| `labelSmall` | 11 w500 ls0.5 | Chips, session buttons (`textMuted`) |
| `statNumber` | 40 w700 | Big metric numbers |

