## Core Widgets (`lib/core/widgets/`)

Always use these instead of raw Material widgets:

- **`AppPrimaryButton`** — full-width 52px, primary bg, glow shadow, built-in loading spinner
- **`AppSecondaryButton`** — outlined variant
- **`AppTextButton`** — text-only, `primary` colour
- **`AppCard`** — `surfaceElevated` bg, `radiusLg`, 1px `border`, 20px padding; use `AppGlowCard` for hero/featured cards
- **`AppTextField`** — styled form field with label
- **`EmptyState`** — icon circle + title + subtitle + optional CTA; always use for empty lists
- **`SectionHeader`** — `headlineSmall` + optional action link
- **`ShimmerBox` / `ShimmerCard` / `ShimmerList`** — skeleton loaders for async content
- **`ResponsiveLayout(maxWidth: 680)`** — wrap all main-tab scroll views

