## Modal / Dialog Patterns

### Bottom sheets
```dart
showModalBottomSheet(
  backgroundColor: AppColors.surface,
  shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.vertical(top: Radius.circular(AppSpacing.radiusXl)),
  ),
  isScrollControlled: true,
  builder: (_) => DraggableScrollableSheet(
    initialChildSize: 0.6, maxChildSize: 0.95, minChildSize: 0.4,
    expand: false,
    builder: (_, ctrl) => SingleChildScrollView(...),
  ),
)
```
Always include a 40×4 drag handle (`AppColors.border`) at the top of the sheet content.

### Centered dialogs
```dart
showDialog(
  barrierColor: AppColors.scrim,
  builder: (_) => Dialog(
    backgroundColor: AppColors.surface,
    shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
      borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(AppSpacing.radiusXl),
      side: BorderSide(color: accentColor.withValues(alpha: 0.25)),
    ),
    insetPadding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 24, vertical: 40),
    child: Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all(AppSpacing.lg), ...),
  ),
)
```

